<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About Us - Mediclaim Info</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
      .gowun-batang-regular {
        font-family: "Gowun Batang", serif;
        font-weight: 400;
        font-style: normal;
      }

      .gowun-batang-bold {
        font-family: "Gowun Batang", serif;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-style: normal;
      }

      body {
        background-color: #f0f8ff;
      }

      .hero-bg {
        background-image: url("https://img.freepik.com/premium-photo/medical-stethoscope-pills-red-heart-blue-background-many-different-medical-objects-light-background-top-view-ai-generated_538213-9245.jpg?w=740");
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        height: 60vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .overlay {
        background: rgba(0, 0, 255, 0.6);
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        z-index: 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body class="text-gray-800 relative">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="hero-bg relative">
      <div class="overlay"></div>
      <div class="relative z-10 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-4 gowun-batang-bold">About Us</h1>
        <p class="text-white text-2xl max-w-2xl mx-auto gowun-batang-regular">
          We provide clear, concise, and reliable information to help you make
          the right medical policy decisions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Who We Are Section -->
    <section class="container mx-auto my-12 px-6">
      <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg p-10">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-6">Who We Are</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 mb-8">
          Welcome to Mediclaim Info! Our mission is to make understanding
          medical policies easier for everyone. We provide clear, concise, and
          accurate information to help you make informed decisions. Navigating
          complex medical jargon is challenging, but with our platform, we
          bridge the gap by offering practical advice in simple language.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-6">Our Vision</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 mb-8">
          Our vision is to create a world where everyone can understand and
          access the right medical policy for their needs. Whether it's
          understanding coverage, benefits, or exclusions, we simplify the
          process so you can choose confidently.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Meet the Team Section -->
    <section class="container mx-auto my-12 px-6">
      <div class="bg-blue-100 shadow-lg rounded-lg p-10">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-6 text-center">
          Meet the Team
        </h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">Atharv</h3>
            <p>
              Atharv brings expertise in healthcare policy, ensuring that the
              content on our platform is accurate and up-to-date, so you always
              get the most relevant information.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">Hrushikesh</h3>
            <p>
              Hrushikesh is our technical mastermind, optimizing the website’s
              performance to ensure a smooth and secure experience for all
              users. He make sure it’s fast and user-friendly.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">Shubham</h3>
            <p>
              Shubham handles content strategy and research, curating articles
              that provide meaningful insights on various policies in
              easy-to-understand language.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">Arnav</h3>
            <p>
              Arnav is our creative lead, focusing on user experience design to
              make our platform visually appealing and user-friendly.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer Section -->
    <footer class="bg-blue-500 text-white py-6">
      <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
        <p class="text-lg">&copy; 2024 Mediclaim Info. All Rights Reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
